narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The course itself is highly dependent on your advisor and your project, so make sure you like and are compatible with both of those things. Professor Casson is administrative. It would make more sense to evaluate my two advisors, Asher Auel and Dhruv Ranganathan. I enjoyed working with them very much; much of my success is due to their consistent support and guidance.
You're completely on your own in terms of departmental support, so lock down an advisor early.
